DISCLAIMER AGAINST GAMBLING HARM

This software is a PARODY. It does not predict EuroMillions draws. EuroMillions
draws are statistically independent and uniformly random; no numerological,
astrological, or pseudo-scientific system can predict them with better than
chance accuracy.

The expected return on EuroMillions is structurally negative (approximately
-50% per euro wagered on average). No system can change this.

If gambling has become a problem for you, please contact Joueurs Info Service
at 09 74 75 13 13 (free call, France) or visit joueurs-info-service.fr.
